---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Lucas Wang">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black uppercase tracking-tighter mb-12 underline decoration-dotted underline-offset-[16px]">
      &gt; WHO_AM_I?
    </h1>
    
    <div class="space-y-12 text-lg leading-relaxed">
      <div class="p-8 border-4 border-[var(--accent)] bg-[var(--background)]">
        <p class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-[var(--accent)]">
          Senior Platform Engineer :: 13+ years experience
        </p>
        <p class="opacity-90">
          I am a Senior Platform Engineer with 13 years of experience building secure, scalable production systems. 
          I specialize in cloud infrastructure, observability, CI/CD automation, and incident response.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <p class="opacity-90 italic p-6 border-l-8 border-[var(--accent)] bg-[var(--foreground)]/5">
        Throughout my career, I have led cross-domain projects encompassing infrastructure, observability, and security with a primary goal of improving the developer experience. I am passionate about building fault-tolerant, self-healing platforms that are intuitive to use, deploy, and operate.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-16 mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--accent)]">&gt; CORE_EXPERTISE</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-[var(--accent)] hover:bg-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--background)] transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter underline">Platform_&_Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold">:: AWS :: Kubernetes :: AWS CDK :: Terraform :: Cloudflare :: Akamai</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-[var(--accent)] hover:bg-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--background)] transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter underline">Observability_Systems</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold">:: Prometheus :: Grafana :: ELK :: New Relic :: Datadog :: OpenTelemetry</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-[var(--accent)] hover:bg-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--background)] transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter underline">CI/CD_&_DevEx</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold">:: GitLab :: Buildkite :: GitHub Actions :: Argo CD :: Backstage</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 border-2 border-dashed border-[var(--accent)] hover:bg-[var(--accent)] hover:text-[var(--background)] transition-all">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-4 text-xl uppercase tracking-tighter underline">Security_&_Quality</h3>
          <p class="text-sm font-bold">:: Orca :: CrowdStrike :: SonarQube :: Snyk :: SOC 2 Compliance</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-16 mb-8 uppercase tracking-widest text-[var(--accent)]">&gt; PHILOSOPHY</h2>
      <p class="opacity-90">
        I believe in "shifting left" whenever possible—integrating security, quality, and observability directly into the platform pipelines. My focus is on enabling product teams to deploy independently and reliably through robust GitOps workflows and automated self-service platforms.
      </p>
      
      <div class="p-6 bg-[var(--accent)] text-[var(--background)] font-bold text-center uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mt-12">
        :: currently based in Adelaide, Australia ::
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
